CMS : Content Management System
It is a tool to create the website and manage the content of the websites dynamically.

Why CMS?
It provides a GUI(Graphical User Interface) with tools to create, edit and pblish web content without the need to write the code from scratch

CMS has 2 components : 
1. Content Management Application (CMA)
2. Content Delivery Application (CDA)

Different CMS Tools:
- WordPress
- Joomla
- Drupal
- CrownPeak
- Tradion
- AEM etc...
